description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As part of our Trusts organisational redesign programme we are now recruiting talented General Managers who will have accountability and responsibility for broad portfolios within our New Planned and Unplanned Care Divisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for ambitious, motivated and compassionate leaders who are committed to providing excellent patient care for our patients and their families. Applicants will be passionate about their own personal and professional development, as well that of their teams and colleagues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful applicants will possess highly developed leadership and interpersonal skills, along with the ability to motivate and build successful teams in a fast paced environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Supported by strong senior leadership teams you will seek, share and drive opportunities to deliver high standards of clinical care whilst ensuring delivery of operational, financial and transformational agenda.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For informal discussion or visit, please contact Dawn Jones - Divisional PA&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dawn Jones  Divisional PA  djones20@nhs.net  01438 286133&lt;/p&gt;
